{
  "stem": "3666.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father had his mother there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And for some sort of reason, she survived until the end.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think my father hid her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I don't know exactly how.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were allowed to exit the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because my father had the paper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were kept for overnight, in some kind of a place-- I don't know what it was, what the name of it was-- where you just sat there and waited until the ghetto was emptied.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then when you returned, the ghetto was emptier, and emptier.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Each time, it was emptier.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then the other hand, I also remember some nice things about the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The people who did stay and who were still in the ghetto, since the element that stayed in the ghetto was a very creative element, there was actually a Philharmonic at the-- at the-- it was an orchestra.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the conductor was Durmashkin, who later died in Klooga, I heard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I met his sisters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had a conservatory of music.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had schools.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They weren't the kind of schools that we all picture now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was schools, where they gathered children and at least introduced some things to them, some culture.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was both.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother-- my parents enrolled me at the Conservatory of Music.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's there that I first touched a piano.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I started, yes, I started.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had a very fine-- they had the best teachers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These teachers were performers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's like studying, starting with people of Juilliard here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Conservatory of Music in Vilna was very known.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Besides Durmashkin there was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was a pianist, her husband was a cellist.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was an opera.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
